Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:43.10,Default1,,0,0,0,,好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:48.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:53.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,都脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:03.12,Default1,,0,0,0,,好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:08.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:18.07,Default1,,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:23.14,Default1,,0,0,0,,好赞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:28.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,好棒喔
