Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:43.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,真的都不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:53.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,合照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:58.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:03.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,那么就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:08.12,Default1,,0,0,0,,先给大家看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:13.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,内裤也要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:18.13,Default1,,0,0,0,,看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:33.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,有点害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:43.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,我是这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:03.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,对这一片的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:18.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,这是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:23.13,Default1,,0,0,0,,挑战呢
