Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:33.14,Default1,,0,0,0,,我们要拍出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:38.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,很棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:43.15,Default1,,0,0,0,,合作片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:48.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,不会让观众失望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:53.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:58.10,Default1,,0,0,0,,来看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:23.12,Default1,,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:28.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,第一次来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:33.13,Default1,,0,0,0,,我们来帮你服务喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:43.14,Default1,,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:48.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:03.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:23.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,更激烈点
